<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40'>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>eTA Canada Application Personal Info</title>
<style>
body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 15px; }
td { padding: 5px; vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 1px solid #cce5ff; }
.label { font-weight: bold; width: 160px; background-color: #e6f2ff; border-right: 1px solid #cce5ff; color: #cc0000; }
.input { color: #000; padding-left: 10px; }
.section-header { background-color: #cc0000; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 8px; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.1em; border-radius: 4px; }
h1 { text-align: center; color: #cc0000; border-bottom: 3px solid #cc0000; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
p.intro { color: #666; text-align: center; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>eTA (Canada) Application Questionnaire (캐나다 eTA 신청서)</h1>
<p class="intro">Please complete all fields carefully. (모든 항목을 영문으로 정확히 기재해주세요.)</p>

<div class="section-header">1. Applicant Information (신청인 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Family Name (성):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Given Name (이름):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Other Names (별명):</td>
        <td class="input">No / Yes (_____________)</td>
        <td class="label">Gender (성별):</td>
        <td class="input">M / F</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Date of Birth (생년월일):</td>
        <td class="input">YYYY-MM-DD</td>
        <td class="label">City of Birth (출생도시):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Country of Birth (출생국):</td>
        <td class="input">South Korea</td>
        <td class="label">Country of Citizenship:</td>
        <td class="input">South Korea</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Marital Status (결혼):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">Single / Married / Separated / Divorced / Widowed / Common-Law</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">2. Passport Information (여권 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Passport Number:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Citizenship ID No:</td>
        <td class="input">(주민번호 뒷자리): ______________</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Issuing Country:</td>
        <td class="input">South Korea</td>
        <td class="label">Issuing Date:</td>
        <td class="input">YYYY-MM-DD</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Expiry Date:</td>
        <td class="input">YYYY-MM-DD</td>
        <td class="label">Other Citizenship:</td>
        <td class="input">No / Yes (Country: _________)</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">3. Contact Information (연락처 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Home Address (주소):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(In English, including Zip Code)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Phone Number:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">Mobile: ____________________ Home: ____________________</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Email Address:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">4. Employment Information (직장 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Occupation:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Employer Name:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Job Title (직위):</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
        <td class="label">Start Year:</td>
        <td class="input"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Address (직장 주소):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">5. Travel Information (여행 정보)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Available Funds (CAD):</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3"></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Date of Travel:</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">(YYYY-MM-DD / HH:MM)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td class="label">Applied/Lived in CA?</td>
        <td class="input" colspan="3">No / Yes (UCI Number? ______________)</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div class="section-header">6. Eligibility Questions (자격 요건 질문)</div>
<table>
    <tr>
        <td colspan="4" style="padding: 10px;">
        1. Ever been refused a visa/permit or ordered to leave Canada or any other country? (비자 거절/입국 거부?) [ ] No [ ] Yes (Details: ________________)<br>
        2. Ever been convicted of a crime? (범죄 경력?) [ ] No [ ] Yes<br>
        3. Have/had tuberculosis or serious health condition? (결핵/건강?) [ ] No [ ] Yes<br>
        4. Syphilis? (매독?) [ ] No [ ] Yes
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<div style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; page-break-inside: avoid;">
    <p>I confirm that the information provided above is true and accurate.</p>
    <br>
    <p><strong>Date (신청일):</strong> _______________________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Signature (서명):</strong> _______________________</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
